{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["A Knight's Promise\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2 - Are You Busy, Commander?<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"After a bit of a hectic start, we finally got the day back on track.","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"At first, U-556 needed a lot of guidance in performing her secretarial duties. But by mid morning she knew what she was doing and was ready to help with a workload a bit heavier than usual.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Hmmhmmhmmm♪～","actor":408040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"She was engrossed in reading some After Action Reports. I decided to let her focus on her work.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Fifteen minutes later...","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ugh, I'm so bored! I thought being secretary ship would be easy and fun. I thought I'd just be playing with the Commander all the time...","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":0,"delay":0,"dur":0.4,"number":2,"x":30}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Heyyyy, Commanderrr! How about we knock off work and go play for a while!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Tactfully decline her offer."}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Awwww!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"U-556 looked a little dejected.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":408040,"bgName":"bg_story_task","withoutActorName":true},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Is this work really that important?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"It seemed like U-556 fundamentally misunderstood the relationship between commander and secretary ship. To her, they were little more than playmates.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Still, the way she took to organizing the office and earnestly focused on her work from dawn until now was certainly praiseworthy... I decided to explain to her the meaning behind our efforts.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Commander? What's wrong? Why do you suddenly look all serious...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I get it now... Without you, the whole port wouldn't be able to function. The Commander's work is really more important than I ever thought...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That's why I gotta help out!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"U-556 seemed like she understood what we were doing. So I took advantage of her enthusiasm and gave her some simple things to work on.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Just hand this over to Akashi down at the shop? I'm on it!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"move","y":0,"delay":1,"dur":0.5,"x":2500}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":408040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"U-556 snatched the document out of my hand and flew out the door.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"It turned out that with the right spirit, she'd be able to handle something like this.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3}},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"......","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"stopbgm":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"But by lunchtime, U-556 still hadn't come back.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"U556STORY2","fadeOut":1.5}